    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. Anno ab incarnacione domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi millesimo centesimo trigesimo quarto, decimo kalendas
                        decembris, indicione duodecima. Constat nos <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #Witness #Landed_possessions #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Venditio"
                                ><name>Bernardum Mazacabai</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #Witness #Landed_possessions #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Venditio"
                                ><name>Froam</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxorem</rs>, qui professi sumus ex nacione nostra lege
                        vivimus <rs key="#Roman">Romana</rs>, accepissemus nos sicuti et in
                        presencia <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs> accepimus a te <persName
                            key="#Priors #Landed_possessions #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Venditio"
                                ><name>Johanne</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">priore</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Venditio"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2071">Sancti Leonardi</orgName> et <rs
                            key="#Monks">monaghus</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monks #Landed_possessions #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Venditio #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti de Arone</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Price">argnetum denariorum bonorum Mediolanensium libras
                            septem</rs>, finito precio sicut inter nos convenit pro <rs key="#Size"
                            >sestariis quindecim <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terre</rs> et
                            [ta]bule octo</rs> intra closuram vestram positam in loco qui nominatur
                            <placeName>Saldine</placeName>, prope Sancta Leonardo. Quas autem
                        iamscriptas sestaria una cum accessionibus et ingressibus eius seu cum
                        superioribus et inferioribus suis, ab hac die iamscripte ecclesie Sancti
                        Benedicti vendimus, tradimus, mancipamus, nulli alii venditas, donatas,
                        obnoxiatas vel traditas nisi predicto monesterio. Et facias exinde <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario nomine</rs> quicquid
                        voluerit sine omni nostra et heredum nostrorum contradicione. Equidem
                        spondemus atque promittimus nos et nostros heredes predicto <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monesterio</rs> aut cui legaliter dederit iamscriptam
                        vendicionem ab omni homine contradicente defendere; quod si defensare non
                        potuerimus aut si predicto monesterio per quodvis ingenium subtraere
                        quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> iamscriptam <rs
                            key="#Venditio">vendicionem</rs> iamscripto monesterio restituamus,
                        sicut pro tempore fuerit meliorata aut valuerit sub estimacione in consimili
                        loco, et nichilt nobis ex ipso precio amplius aliquid dare debes dicimus,
                        cum stipulacionc subnixa. Actum <placeName>Parma</placeName>. Feliciter.
                        (S.) Signa manuum iamscriptorum iugalium, qui hanc cartulam fieri
                        rogaverunt. (S.) Signa manuum <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"
                                ><name>Omnibene</name></persName> de Cremo, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Iohannes/Gusie">Iohannis
                                Gusie</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"
                                ><name>Bonifilii</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name>Ardingi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name>Iohanni Borri</name></persName>
                        Benedicte, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Alberti</name></persName> rogati testes. (SN) <rs key="#Writer"
                            >Scripsi</rs> ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Venditio"
                                ><name>Mainfredus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri palacii hanc cartulam post traditam
                        compievi. </ab>
